üü¢ Quick Revision Table
Formula	Output
TODAY()	Date
NOW()	Date + Time
YEAR()	Year
MONTH()	Month number
DAY()	Day
üü° Important Notes

Dates must be valid Excel dates

TODAY & NOW update automatically

Use Paste Special ‚Üí Values to freeze dates

